column1: # Required | Three-letter IATA code for destination airport.
column2: # Required | Three-letter IATA code for origin airport.
column5: # Optional | A short; relevant description of the flight. Include specific or unique details. Use plain text and don't enter text in all capital letters. Character limit: 5;000.
column8: # Optional | The URL of the specific page where people can view the flight.
column10: # Optional | The cost and currency of a one way flight. The price is a number followed by the 3-digit currency code (ISO 4217 standards). Use a period (".") as the decimal point.
column11: # Optional | Used by advertisers to mark priority of flight. Can be used to create product set of distressed flights
